rsion in a number of different forms: <i>Mattan(i)ah</i>, <i>Mattatha(h)</i>, <i>Mattithiah</i>, <i>Mattathias</i>, and so on. In the Authorized Version, the evangelist is regularly referred to as <i>Matthew</i>, while the apostle chosen to replace Judas Iscariot is distinguished as   Matthias .  A related name from the same Hebrew roots, but reversed, is   Jonathan .  Throughout the English-speaking world <i>Matthew</i> has been particularly popular since the 1970s."],"variants":[{"name":"Mathew","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Matthew ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"MATTHEW WHITFIELD was born in 1327, in Whitfield, Northumberland, England, United Kingdom as the son of JOHN WHITFIELD. He had at least 2 sons. He died in 1385, in England, United Kingdom, at the age of 58."},"et":{"1327–1385":"1327–1385","1360–Male":"1360–Surnud","1348–1414":"1348–1414","1310–1370":"1310–1370","1327":"1327","1414":"1414","1348":"1348","1310":"1310","1385":"1385","1360":"1360","1370":"1370","Whitfield Hall, Northumberland, England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1327–1385":"1327–1385","1360–Male":"1360–Kuollut","1348–1414":"1348–1414","1310–1370":"1310–1370","1327":"1327","1414":"1414","1348":"1348","1310":"1310","1385":"1385","1360":"1360","1370":"1370","Whitfield Hall, Northumberland, England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1327–1385":"1327–1385","1360–Male":"1360–Décédé","1348–1414":"1348–1414","1310–1370":"1310–1370","1327":"1327","1414":"1414","1348":"1348","1310":"1310","1385":"1385","1360":"1360","1370":"1370","Whitfield Hall, Northumberland, England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"MATTHEW WHITFIELD est né en 1327, à Whitfield, Northumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de JOHN WHITFIELD. Il a eu au moins 2 fils. Il est décédé en 1385, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 58 ans."},"de":{"1327–1385":"1327–1385","1360–Male":"1360–Verstorben","1348–1414":"1348–1414","1310–1370":"1310–1370","1327":"1327","1414":"1414","1348":"1348","1310":"1310","1385":"1